---
title: Sesame Chicken Schnitzel & Corn-Studded Rice with Japanese Aioli & Sweet Chilli Veggies
description: How do you dress up schnitzel and rice, by decking them out in some bling! The chicken is cooked with a scattering of sesame seeds studded like jewels and then drizzled in a Japanese aioli. The rice is also bedazzled tonight with bright pops of corn. It’s sure to dazzle your tastebuds.
